{"tid":1961450,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[痴撚線公司] 如果食左肺炎動物肉會點","createTime":"2020-04-06T20:24:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T03:19:25.000Z","uid":7427,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c5c4f0c5052fc81aff4a465a452f9bb7581eb802","tid":1961450,"uid":7427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T20:24:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FtFCSsw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFtFCSsw.png&h=467921bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%B4%90%E7%B4%84%E5%8B%95%E7%89%A9%E5%9C%92%E8%80%81%E8%99%8E%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E9%A6%96%E4%BE%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E7%25B4%2590%25E7%25B4%2584%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%2589%25A9%25E5%259C%2592%25E8%2580%2581%25E8%2599%258E%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA-%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E9%25A6%2596%25E4%25BE%258B%2F&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2le%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=70d5f57b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E7%25B4%2590%25E7%25B4%2584%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%2589%25A9%25E5%259C%2592%25E8%2580%2581%25E8%2599%258E%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA-%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E9%25A6%2596%25E4%25BE%258B%2F&h=d3c82e7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%B4%90%E7%B4%84%E5%8B%95%E7%89%A9%E5%9C%92%E8%80%81%E8%99%8E%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E9%A6%96%E4%BE%8B/</a><br />\n<br />\n當年沙士都好嚴重 <br />\n但係小弟無聽過人傳動物<br />\n最初武漢肺炎傳動物既case係馬主隻狗<br />\n之後到貓 今日就到老虎<br />\n我相信日後極大可能性傳到去&quot;食用動物&quot;<br />\n諗深一層 其實好撚得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果武漢肺炎可以人傳動物 <br />\n咁會唔會動物傳動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n動物中肺炎 又會唔會發生異變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假如豬牛雞中左肺炎既肉流入市面<br />\n又或者支那人又走去搞中左肺炎既野味<br />\n<br />\n人類食左呢啲肺炎肉到底會發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">會唔會好似netflix套李屍朝鮮咁</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nC4wcAf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnC4wcAf.jpg&h=3734d814&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bcc7c9315d28a58177af6785d97fcd7a91694506","tid":1961450,"uid":258578,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T20:24:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dfaeee1375c06a10618aa796fdeea7258813b088","tid":1961450,"uid":7427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcc7c9315d28a58177af6785d97fcd7a91694506","tid":1961450,"uid":258578,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T20:24:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T20:25:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9443735fc47ec1b602e520c9f74f60e3b88d7bb8","tid":1961450,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T20:26:59.000Z","msg":"人類要轉食草"},{"pid":"df4e9c38cc5da54705ad87f3e325608b71080210","tid":1961450,"uid":143260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcc7c9315d28a58177af6785d97fcd7a91694506","tid":1961450,"uid":258578,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T20:24:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T20:27:41.000Z","msg":"好好笑ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f976beb4b43952cd030c8e46c1b1293914c113","tid":1961450,"uid":7427,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"9443735fc47ec1b602e520c9f74f60e3b88d7bb8","tid":1961450,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTim